===Specifications=== *Processor: [[Realtek]] RTL8392M Multi-Layer Managed Switch :Controller with Embedded MIPS 34Kc @700MHz *Co-processor: [[STMicro]] STM32F100C8 to manage PoE *Flash/RAM: 16MB (SPI NOR) Flash, 128MB RAM (DDR3) *8x Gigabit Ethernet PoE+ ports *2x Shared Gigabit Ethernet/SFP Slots *180W PoE budget *20Gbps Switching Capacity
